Q37. What is the output?
class Base:
    def __init__(self):
        self.__secret = "base"
class Derived(Base):
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__()
        self.__secret = "derived"
    def show(self):
        print(self.__secret)
        print(self._Base__secret)
Derived().show()
A:
derived
base
Two different mangled attributes coexist.
